Linux::hddtemp 0.01
===================

Linux::hddtemp monitors hard disk temperatures using the hddtemp
utility for Linux.

INSTALLATION

 To install this module type the following:

   perl Build.pl
   ./Build
   ./Build test
   ./Build install
   
 Or, if you're on a platform (like DOS or Windows) that doesn't
 like  the "./" notation, you can do this:

   perl Build.PL
   perl Build
   perl Build test
   perl Build install


DEPENDENCIES

  perl
  IO::Socket
  hddtemp run in daemon mode,
    see http://www.guzu.net/linux/hddtemp.php


